@node "wasmacht" ""

 RandomStartup selects a random startup-sequence to boot. WHY THAT? I give
 you an example: You have installed several bootintros, but if you see
 the same bootintro with the same music every day you`ll hate it after 2 weeks.
 But if you`ve 10 bootintros installed and RandomStartup selects one of
 it every time when you boot you`ve alternation at your bootup.

 So don`t wait any longer - click on to Install and have fun!
 
@endnode

